title: The Snacket
description: Katie and Ashley's second bracket of Third Month Crazy Time raises the stakes when they crown the King of Bagged Snacks (12:08). There's also our last Bachelor Update of the season (45:30), a Very Cavallari Update (53:23), a brief Whiskey Cavalier update (3:50), and a not-to-be-missed Miley Cyrus moment (1:21:51).
